Name: Sky of Destruction
About the game: Sky of Destruction is a top-down shooter created by a team of two people. Before starting a mission, select a combination of three types of aircraft in your fleet, which will help you during the mission. Your goal is to destroy the enemy aircraft carrier or buildings, breaking through the enemy air armada. Switch between planes during the mission. Put items in the most effective way. Enjoy the juicy explosions of enemy buildings and their physical destruction. Explosions and total destruction!
